Hey all, we thought this would be a different way to announce the launch of our Off the Dock Toons licensed T-shirt designs.  Here is the link to our newly launched T-shirts - Off the Dock Toons T-shirt Designs   Please check them out!  The Contest I am posting a picture of a Largemouth and Smallmouth bass I caught.  The 2 members who guess the closest to the actual weight of BOTH THESE FISH COMBINED will win an original OTD shirt posted below. I have sent the weight to TJ. No duplicate weights.  This contest will run until Sunday August 22 @ 6pm.  Here is the picture, take a guess at the weight of these two fish combined - Example 0.00lbs  I am 6'3, 215lbs.   Here are your choices of Shirt designs. Shirt One Shirt Two Shirt Three - Kids  Good Luck.
